01:38:35,330 --> 01:38:39,370
I'll stay here with my daughter
and wait for you.

824
01:38:39,580 --> 01:38:41,280
Dad, go back first.

825
01:38:41,490 --> 01:38:43,510
You have no idea how barbaric they are.

826
01:38:43,720 --> 01:38:47,480
Don't be afraid.
I won't leave until they rescue you.

827
01:38:48,100 --> 01:38:50,090
Okay. But you must stay here
no matter what.

828
01:38:50,290 --> 01:38:52,630
We'll be back within three days
to take you away.

829
01:38:55,410 --> 01:38:57,360
Let them through.

830
01:39:00,980 --> 01:39:02,410
Director, you can take care of them.

831
01:39:02,610 --> 01:39:03,760
You must make sure they are safe.

832
01:39:03,970 --> 01:39:05,600
Don't worry. I promise.

833
01:39:08,530 --> 01:39:10,550
Discuss this with the other family.

834
01:39:10,750 --> 01:39:12,560
It's best to find a peaceful solution.

835
01:39:12,980 --> 01:39:15,520
It's easy to solve.
My daughter-in-law stays.

836
01:39:15,720 --> 01:39:16,980
Okay.

837
01:39:22,820 --> 01:39:24,390
Move out of the way.

838
01:39:25,580 --> 01:39:26,750
Let them go.

839
01:39:26,960 --> 01:39:28,990
Please let them pass.

840
01:40:05,860 --> 01:40:08,610
Please, stop! Where are you taking her?

841
01:40:08,820 --> 01:40:09,620
We're not going anywhere.

842
01:40:10,700 --> 01:40:12,020
It's okay, they'll only be gone two days.

843
01:40:12,230 --> 01:40:13,180
No way.

844
01:40:13,870 --> 01:40:16,500
We're not leaving.

845
01:40:16,710 --> 01:40:20,470
Get out of the way.
We have to leave today.

846
01:40:20,680 --> 01:40:23,880
- No matter what.
- No way! Don't hit her!

847
01:40:24,170 --> 01:40:25,040
Who cares!

848
01:40:25,350 --> 01:40:26,890
Don't hit her! We're not leaving.

849
01:40:27,090 --> 01:40:29,040
You want to wait for the police
to rescue you?

850
01:40:29,280 --> 01:40:30,300
No way!

851
01:40:30,600 --> 01:40:32,160
We'll stay! Don't hit her!

852
01:40:32,370 --> 01:40:33,100
She's my wife, for the rest of her life!

853
01:40:33,310 --> 01:40:35,860
Help! Please!

854
01:40:36,060 --> 01:40:37,070
Don't hit her!

855
01:40:37,270 --> 01:40:39,990
Don't hit her!

856
01:40:41,000 --> 01:40:49,640
Someone! Help!

